text: Mamyakovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Sharipovsky Selsoviet, Kushnarenkovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 437 as of 2010. There are 12 streets. == Geography == It is located 24 km from Kushnarenkovo, 6 km from Sharipovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kushnarenkovsky District
title: Mamyakovo
